thread.title_full: Viking Bags reviewed by Anthony Kucharczyk

author: Anthony Kucharczyk
title: Anthony Kucharczyk
text: So far I like the quality. Received everything I needed to install them. I did modify the mounting arms because I have the back rest but they look fine. But because of it being winter I won't be able to take a trip til spring. But I like the look of them.
